thread.title: Treasury Plans to Sell $130 Billion in Debt

author: wsjcom
title: Treasury Plans to Sell $130 Billion in Debt
text:
The U.S. Treasury Department will auction $130 billion in securities next week, comprising $42 billion in new debt and $88 billion in previously sold debt. Details (all with minimum denominations of $100):
Tuesday: $40 billion in four-week bills, a reopening of an issue first sold on Dec. 28, 2017, maturing June 28, 2018. Cusip number: 912796PM5.
